{"tid":2314540,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手貓奴 想問下問題","createTime":"2020-12-06T15:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T10:23:44.000Z","uid":87582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"235e840245c8b09b7107c3475937e6f8d598b451","tid":2314540,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好<br />\n隻貓2個月個陣接返屋企<br />\n已經好愛好痴人<br />\n返左黎一星期度<br />\n依兩日爬上你身會抓你咬你<br />\n輕輕惡又唔聽<br />\n知佢想抓野<br />\n買左啲麻繩玩具 甚至落埋貓粉都唔玩 聞完會避開 但佢就係中意咬你手指 同捉你手指 <br />\n平時地下玩唔會 上到身先會<br />\n但頭幾日無野 上到身會好乖仲會煲晒水咁<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下如果有啲地方唔去佢爬去<br />\n例如門口地氈 應該點教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家叫佢名會有少少反應 但好少好少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求救"},{"pid":"145010e23de68425e516ebf818366a1a5e79bee5","tid":2314540,"uid":73907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"相都冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1bef924563b9484403ddb81ea93b8b3fa961f4","tid":2314540,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZCEggN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZCEggN.jpg&h=6e6e96b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買呢種紙皮製既貓抓板<br />\n<br />\n貓粉佢唔鍾意就唔好再落"},{"pid":"db7b669a43a611b986a0b976b5f35b6a4b2d7f68","tid":2314540,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb1bef924563b9484403ddb81ea93b8b3fa961f4","tid":2314540,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZCEggN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZCEggN.jpg&h=6e6e96b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買呢種紙皮製既貓抓板<br />\n<br />\n貓粉佢唔鍾意就唔好再落"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2