"hkgmoji\" />大家好<br />\n隻貓2個月個陣接返屋企<br />\n已經好愛好痴人<br />\n返左黎一星期度<br />\n依兩日爬上你身會抓你咬你<br />\n輕輕惡又唔聽<br />\n知佢想抓野<br />\n買左啲麻繩玩具 甚至落埋貓粉都唔玩 聞完會避開 但佢就係中意咬你手指 同捉你手指 <br />\n平時地下玩唔會 上到身先會<br />\n但頭幾日無野 上到身會好乖仲會煲晒水咁<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下如果有啲地方唔去佢爬去<br />\n例如門口地氈 應該點教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家叫佢名會有少少反應 但好少好少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求救"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"佢寵幸你先咬你<br />\n你要感到榮幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0117cf74188a1c894f65a3d33a4aee6887d3ec","tid":2314540,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23911206a49da94109658b0b65f7817ea167ebfe","tid":2314540,"uid":243180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"235e840245c8b09b7107c3475937e6f8d598b451","tid":2314540,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家好<br />\n隻貓2個月個陣接返屋企<br />\n已經好愛好痴人<br />\n返左黎一星期度<br />\n依兩日爬上你身會抓你咬你<br />\n輕輕惡又唔聽<br />\n知佢想抓野<br />\n買左啲麻繩玩具 甚至落埋貓粉都唔玩 聞完會避開 但佢就係中意咬你手指 同捉你手指 <br />\n平時地下玩唔會 上到身先會<br />\n但頭幾日無野 上到身會好乖仲會煲晒水咁<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下如果有啲地方唔去佢爬去<br />\n例如門口地氈 應該點教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家叫佢名會有少少反應 但好少好少<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求救"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"佢寵幸你先咬你<br />\n你要感到榮幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天氣乾 一咬一抓就損晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ecf2aa9e69babc8ab77007877cd67c1ea071a3","tid":2314540,"uid":232400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:37:13.000Z","msg":"細貓一定好鐘意咬人<br />\n因為佢當左你啲手腳係獵物 同埋出牙仔<br />\n如果佢咬你就大叫No! 唔準！<br />\n惡啲既語氣比佢知道你唔鐘意 要慢慢教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外我隻貓一開始都唔玩貓抓板同柱 <br />\n係有一日無啦啦開始識用 所以都無得強迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好方法就多啲用逗貓棒同佢消耗體力 <br />\n比佢狩獵下啲玩具 唔好用手指同佢玩 <br />\n玩到佢倦晒就少啲咬人<br />\n<br />\n另外2個月大既幼貓對呢啲貓粉貓薄荷無咩反應<br />\n大大下就識玩嫁啦 慢慢來呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7613253dd6802af83621e32fc7c19697ffbb69cf","tid":2314540,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69629e4adbf8bbcf679c0700bb91223272515763","tid":2314540,"uid":228894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T06:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v92Emox.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv92Emox.gif&h=29567c02&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a1d4f6b6d3602221063d012e04c39ddd98f26ae","tid":2314540,"uid":112645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b3dfd41d6ce56222b3757fd2b3e936bf78fecc3","tid":2314540,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff4b0273e745a90b99a0e9a09498b4c0df2680d3","tid":2314540,"uid":112645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T18:12:29.000Z","msg":"我可唔可以搭單問<br />\n<br />\n執到隻貓唔肯定幾大 獸醫話可能2-4個月都有可能<br />\n<br />\n佢頭兩日好乖好似公仔咁<br />\n依家已經跑跑跳跳好活潑....<br />\n次次一見到我就撲我小腿<br />\n有時會咬我<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔痛 但係想知道佢點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />生緊牙仔 癢想搵野咬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來係咁<br />\n咁係咪由得佢咬？<br />\n但係佢又唔咬屋企啲嘢"},{"pid":"5229a5b43e5ce6d8e8c73f19c40275e53158fc19","tid":2314540,"u